Your Five Minute Journal entries will now auto save as you go. If you exit the app before you re quite finished your unfinished entry will be waiting for you when you return! A small bug with editing entries featuring an image has now been resolved. The terms of service button wasn t working for some iOS 10 users due to some system changes. This is now fixed!
